* Name: Place Rush Order
* Brief description: This use case describes the interactions between the AIMS software with the customer when the customer desires to place rush order
* Precondition: Only addresses in Hanoi City are supported
* Postcondition: None
* Basic flow
	1. The AIMS Software checks if there is media and the shipping address are supported to place rush order
	2. The software changes the formula to calculate the shipping fees
* Alternative flow
	1.1. If there is no support, notify the customer and ask customer to update delivery information Or, the software lets customer to update rush order info
